Package: xinx
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xinx-scripts
Description: XSL/JS/HTML editor for Generix
 XINX is an editor of XSL stylesheet, JavaScript, Cascading Style Sheet.
 This editor is used with egx.

